Title: Mind Games
Plot: Gibbs is ordered to talk to a convict that is about to be executed, in order to discover information about the place where he hid his victims, but when the plan doesn't work, the team must solve the case in their own way.
ParentalRatingReason: R13 Violence and content that may disturb
Writer: Jeffrey A. Kirkpatrick, John C. Kelley
GuestStars: Jessica Steen, Lawrence Monoson, Chad Donella, Tom Wright, Scott Williamson, Christopher Shyer
